Pre-Event

  Contract Stuff
    1) Verbal Agreement
    2) Contract Sent
    3) Contract Signed
    4) Down Payment

  Venue
    1) Location Identified
    2) Location Confirmed
    3) Permissions and Insurance
    4) Signed Contract 
    5) Down Payment







Post-Event

  Contract
    1) Send invoice (with applicable surcharges)
    2) Collect Final Payment 
    3) Send confirmation of payment receipt to client
    4) Send hand written thank you note(s) to client(s)

  Venue
    1) Final Payment
    2) Thank you note
